Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  小圆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达也去叫她了  去帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
